<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>PrankStar - Spreading Laughter</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #E6EFFF;
    }
    .brand-heading {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem; /* Responsive font size */
    }
    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem; /* Responsive font size */
    }
    .custom-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 0.125rem 0.25rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="brand-heading">PrankStar</h1>
        <p class="lead">The best pranks in State College!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
          <img src="images/prankstar-logo-but-better.png" class="img-fluid" alt="PrankStar logo">
        </div>
        <div class="custom-card p-4">
          <p>Hello, and welcome to PrankStar! With a team of creative masterminds, PrankStar is committed to delivering carefully curated pranks for each client. Founded in 2023, we are passionate about spreading laughter via (mostly) harmless mischief in the State College area! (Not liable for damages)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
